        "text_prKfLD": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Tre is a brand established to provide home essentials crafted from clean, safe, and natural materials, offering sustainable quality designed to last for years.</p><p>As we began exploring ways to enhance the health and well-being of our homes and families, we realized that a truly holistic healthy lifestyle goes far beyond just dietary choices. There are small, invisible elements that affect our health cumulatively, often without us even noticing or realizing it. Once we understood that simple decisions in the kitchen and throughout the home make a profound difference, we felt a responsibility we simply could not ignore.</p><p>From this sense of duty, <strong>Tre</strong> was born a brand dedicated to education and awareness, providing safe, healthy, and practical essentials characterized by high quality and ease of use. Packed by our commitment to user satisfaction and products warranty. We believe that making conscious choices shouldn’t be complicated, and that every home deserves essentials you can truly trust.</p><p>We believe in a holistic, conscious, and healthy lifestyle. This principle guides every detail within Tre from the selection of materials and products to the messages and content we share to raise awareness within our community. In our debut collection, we are proud to present a range of stainless steel cookware, crafted to the highest specifications and rigorous standards. These pieces are designed to be daily essentials that will accompany you for years to come.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
